      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>So we being different from those Warehouse <FONT color=#a82424>Clones</FONT>is not being done on purpose.<BR>So what are those <FONT color=#a82424>Clones</FONT>called again?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-g" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Misunderstood?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>I might have said something strange now.<BR>Anyway people tend to misunderstand my family members.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-h" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Yes. They tell this kind of lies. We are <FONT color=#a82424>fussy crooks, </FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>dwarfs,</FONT>, and we break weapons during enhancement, <FONT color=#a82424>siphon off epic loot.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-1-i" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The fussy part seems true...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>I won't hesitate to say this. Those rumors are not reliable at all. Their credibility is <FONT color=#a82424>0%</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
